{"tid":1734880,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"響理大就等於有份暴動？好難講","createTime":"2019-11-18T12:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T17:27:26.000Z","uid":10546,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"57bd4d73e3505797ec674777347e3e3b22c87e95","tid":1734880,"uid":10546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"首先，千祈唔好自首，自首左個file 就寫明自首就乜撚都唔使玩，<br />\n<br />\n響PolyU 既，即刻換衫，衫褲鞋襪全換，有幾遠掉幾遠，有魔法既都要掉，淨低d 囗罩就算鳩數。<br />\n<br />\nIn case 真係強攻比人拉既，記撚住乜撚都唔好講，佢無料揸手證明到你響理大出黎 = 有份阻路擲磚頭，最多告到非法集結，比cam 影哂既自求多福，總知有律師先好夾點樣講，唔係乜撚都唔好講，手足響差館都係。<br />\n<br />\n最後，衰d 都要講，搵定星火夾律師先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cc1b68e2d47e07b0f0911f11cd268752f71c64","tid":1734880,"uid":248364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"自修去圖書館溫左幾日書，路又封晒走唔到，關咩暴動事？"},{"pid":"30a8c09eed2237dbb238b135f442c02c1ec91849","tid":1734880,"uid":112171,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"咁有朝一日有人佔咗狗宿，咁裡面啲狗仔狗女係唔係都係暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7373d1deb1a85178ea8c0b17a431f2ef212c39","tid":1734880,"uid":165028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"86cc1b68e2d47e07b0f0911f11cd268752f71c64","tid":1734880,"uid":248364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"自修去圖書館溫左幾日書，路又封晒走唔到，關咩暴動事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"都話好多唔係poly學生"},{"pid":"66c15ba941e718f4ee2348f5afd0927096dee5e2","tid":1734880,"uid":10546,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"db7373d1deb1a85178ea8c0b17a431f2ef212c39","tid":1734880,"uid":165028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"86cc1b68e2d47e07b0f0911f11cd268752f71c64","tid":1734880,"uid":248364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"自修去圖書館溫左幾日書，路又封晒走唔到，關咩暴動事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T12:29:30.000Z","ms